   205â†’REQUIRED:
   206â†’1. In OBSERVE phase, build 3-10 ISC criteria
   207â†’2. Write criteria to ISC.json before proceeding
   208â†’3. Each criterion: 8-12 words, binary testable STATE
   209â†’
   210â†’Example criterion: "Research agents return findings within two minutes"
   211â†’
   212â†’Fix the ISC.json and try again.`;
   213â†’  }
   214â†’
   215â†’  if (validationResult.valid && result.warnings.length === 0) {
   216â†’    console.error('[ISCValidator] âś“ All validation checks passed');
   217â†’  }
   218â†’
   219â†’  return result;
   220â†’}
