   206â†’    /\*+đźŽŻ\s*COMPLETED:\*+\s*\[AGENT:(\w+[-\w]*)\]\s*(.+?)(?:\n|$)/is,
   207â†’    /\*+đźŽŻ\s+COMPLETED:\*+\s*\[AGENT:(\w+[-\w]*)\]\s*(.+?)(?:\n|$)/is,
